products.description: The Eureka Mignon Manuale represents the perfect entry point into Eureka's renowned Mignon series of espresso grinders. The manual dosing system operates with a simple push of your portafilter against the activation button, allowing for hands-free operation while you grind exactly the amount you need. Built with the same attention to detail as Eureka's higher-end models, the Manuale features a sturdy aluminum body and high-quality internal components. The 300g bean hopper is removable and can be closed off, making it easy to switch between different coffees. At just 12cm wide, it fits comfortably on any kitchen counter. Available in classic matte black or white finishes, the Mignon Manuale proves that you don't need to compromise on quality to stay within budget. It's the ideal grinder for those beginning their espresso journey or upgrading from blade grinders, offering commercial-grade performance in a compact, user-friendly package.

The elegant wood or concrete handle not only adds aesthetic appeal but also enhances the feel of the tamp, ensuring a comfortable and effective espresso preparation experience. Disclaimer: Only the handle is included; the tamper base is sold separately.
